  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are the best Magento pop up extensions out there? Both free and paid?",
  "response": "Magento offers a variety of pop-up extensions that can enhance user engagement, capture leads, promote sales, and improve overall site functionality. Here are some of the best pop-up extensions available, both free and paid:\n\n### Free Extensions\n\n1. **MagePal Pop Up Extension**  \n   - **Features**: Simple pop-up creator, schedule pop-ups, customize look and feel.\n   - **Use Case**: Great for basic notifications and announcements.\n\n2. **Rokanthemes Pop-Up**  \n   - **Features**: User-friendly interface, multiple pop-up types, and customization options.\n   - **Use Case**: Useful for newsletter subscriptions and promotional announcements.\n\n3. **NMC Popup**  \n   - **Features**: Easy to set up, customizable design, support for HTML content.\n   - **Use Case**: Ideal for basic marketing strategies and user engagement.\n\n### Paid Extensions\n\n1. **Aheadworks Popup & Notification**  \n   - **Price**: Around $99  \n   - **Features**: Highly customizable templates, advanced targeting options, A/B testing.\n   - **Use Case**: Suitable for sophisticated marketing campaigns and lead generation.\n\n2. **MageWorx Gift Wrap Popup**  \n   - **Price**: Approximately $149  \n   - **Features**: Offers gift wrap options in pop-ups, fully customizable, enhanced user experience.\n   - **Use Case**: Perfect for stores looking to add a gifting option at checkout.\n\n3. **Landofcoder Popup Pro**  \n   - **Price**: About $89  \n   - **Features**: Various display types (e.g., modal, slide, top), cookie management, rich targeting rules.\n   - **Use Case**: Best for comprehensive lead generation and customer interaction strategies.\n\n4. **Webkul Popup Builder**  \n   - **Price**: Starts around $69  \n   - **Features**: Drag-and-drop interface, various pop-up types (email capture, exit intent, etc.), customizable.\n   - **Use Case**: Ideal for users wanting complete control over their pop-up design and functionality.\n\n5. **MGS Mega Menu with Popup**  \n   - **Price**: Approximately $79  \n   - **Features**: Integrates pop-ups with mega menu functionality, responsive design, and customization settings.\n   - **Use Case**: Useful for stores looking to enhance navigation while using pop-up capabilities.\n\n### Considerations When Choosing a Pop-Up Extension:\n\n- **Purpose**: Determine the main goal (e.g., lead capture, announcements, promotions).\n- **Customization**: Look for options that allow extensive customization to fit your store design.\n- **User Experience**: Ensure the pop-up is non-intrusive and enhances the shopping experience.\n- **Compatibility**: Confirm compatibility with your current Magento version and other extensions.\n- **Support**: Opt for extensions with good support and regular updates.\n\nBefore installing any extension, it's advisable to check user reviews, documentation, and test compatibility in a staging environment to ensure optimal performance on your Magento store.",
